    • copyToClipboard

      public static net.md_5.bungee.api.chat.ClickEvent copyToClipboard(@Nonnull String copy)
      Generates a copy to clipboard click event. COPY_TO_CLIPBOARD will copy text to the player's clipboard.

      This directly copies the text to the player's clipboard without any notification, so suggestCommand(String) could be more useful as it provides visual feedback.

      Parameters:
      copy - - Text to copy.
      Returns:
      COPY_TO_CLIPBOARD ClickEvent.
